<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Cozy Coffee | Holmen, WI</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f8f3ee;
    color:#4a3628;
}

header{
    background:#5d4037;
    color:white;
    padding:20px 8%;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

header h1{
    font-size:32px;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-left:20px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
    height:85vh;
    background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.45),rgba(0,0,0,.45)),
    url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80");
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
}

.hero h2{
    font-size:55px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:22px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
    background:#d8a56d;
    color:white;
    padding:15px 30px;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

section{
    padding:70px 8%;
}

h3{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:36px;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    text-align:center;
}

.hours{
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.hours p{
    margin:10px 0;
}

footer{
    background:#5d4037;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>☕ Cozy Coffee</h1>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#hours">Hours</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<div>
<h2>Welcome to Cozy Coffee</h2>
<p>Fresh Coffee • Homemade Bakery • Friendly Smiles</p>
<a href="#menu" class="btn">View Menu</a>
</div>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h3>About Us</h3>

<p style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:auto;font-size:18px;line-height:1.8;">
At Cozy Coffee in Holmen, Wisconsin, we believe every cup should feel like home.
Whether you're grabbing your morning latte, meeting a friend, or enjoying a fresh bakery treat,
our welcoming atmosphere makes every visit special.
</p>

</section>

<section id="menu">

<h3>Customer Favorites</h3>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h4>☕ Specialty Lattes</h4>
<p>Hot or iced handcrafted espresso drinks.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h4>🥐 Fresh Bakery</h4>
<p>Homemade pastries baked fresh daily.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h4>🥪 Breakfast Sandwiches</h4>
<p>Perfect for your morning coffee run.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h4>🍓 Smoothies</h4>
<p>Refreshing fruit smoothies for every season.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="hours">

<h3>Hours</h3>

<div class="hours">

<p><strong>Monday – Friday</strong><br>5:30 AM – 5:30 PM</p>

<p><strong>Saturday</strong><br>7:00 AM – 3:00 PM</p>

<p><strong>Sunday</strong><br>8:00 AM – 1:00 PM</p>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">

<h3>Visit Us</h3>

<p style="text-align:center;font-size:20px;line-height:2;">
📍 515 Amy Drive, Holmen, WI 54636<br>
📞 (608) 399-3042
</p>

</section>

<footer>

<h3 style="color:white;margin-bottom:10px;">Cozy Coffee</h3>

<p>Serving Holmen one cup at a time ☕</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
